<p>The above market analysis is based on public information and macroeconomic logic, intended for informational purposes only. Macroeconomic trends and financial market performance are influenced by a complex array of unpredictable factors, including but not limited to geopolitical conflicts, sudden policy shifts, technological revolution impacts, and extreme market sentiment. The content of this article does not constitute any specific investment advice or decision-making basis. Investors should make independent judgments based on their own risk tolerance, investment objectives, and financial situation, and are advised to consult a professional financial advisor. Markets involve risks; investing requires caution.</p><div class="disclaimer" style="margin-top:2em;padding:1em 1.2em;border-radius:8px;background:rgba(100,116,139,0.1);border:1px solid rgba(100,116,139,0.2);font-size:0.8em;color:#94a3b8;"><p><strong>Disclaimer</strong></p><p>This article is for informational purposes only and does not constitute investment advice. Financial markets involve risks; investing requires caution. Data and opinions are current as of the time of writing and may change with market developments.</p></div><div class="cta-block" style="margin-top:1em;padding:1.5em;border-radius:12px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(59,130,246,0.1),rgba(16,185,129,0.1));border:1px solid rgba(59,130,246,0.2);"><p><strong>Begin Your Trading Journey</strong></p><p>Yayapay provides secure and convenient global asset trading services.<a href="https://invest.biyapay.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="color:#3b82f6;font-weight:bold;"> Register Now →</a></p></div>', 'https://images.pexels.com/photos/31536334/pexels-photo-31536334.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&h=650&w=940', 1, NULL, NULL, 'YayaNews', 'published', 'deep', 0, '2026-04-07 12:48:01', '2026-04-08 18:41:41', '2026-04-08 18:41:41', '2026-04-08 18:41:41', 'en', 'neutral', '^GSPC', '', 'YayaNews', '', '', 'approved') ON CONFLI