<p>Beyond Arbitrum and Optimism, other Layer2 networks like zkSync and StarkNet will also benefit. Reports indicate that all rollup-based Layer2 solutions can leverage the data availability improvements from the Cancun upgrade to reduce operational costs. This may intensify competition across the entire Layer2 landscape, driving innovation towards lower fees and higher scalability.</p>
