ity. Investors should make prudent decisions and exercise independent judgment.</p><div class="disclaimer" style="margin-top:2em;padding:1em 1.2em;border-radius:8px;background:rgba(100,116,139,0.1);border:1px solid rgba(100,116,139,0.2);font-size:0.8em;color:#94a3b8;"><p><strong>Disclaimer</strong></p><p>This article synthesizes content from public information sources such as RSS feeds. It is provided for informational purposes only and does not constitute any investment advice. Financial markets carry risks; invest with caution. Data and opinions herein are current as of the time of writing and may change with market developments.</p></div><div class="cta-block" style="margin-top:1em;padding:1.5em;border-radius:12px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(59,130,246,0.1),rgba(16,185,129,0.1));border:1px solid rgba(59,130,246,0.2);"><p><strong>Begin Your Trading Journey</strong></p><p>Yayapay provides secure and convenient global asset trading services.<a href="https://invest.biyapay.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="color:#3b82f6;font-weight:bold;"> Register Now →</a></p></div>', 'https://images.pexels.com/photos/10165700/pexels-photo-10165700.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&h=650&w=940', 1, NULL, NULL, 'YayaNews', 'published', 'standard', 0, '2026-04-07 11:47:40', '2026-04-08 18:59:21', '2026-04-08 18:59:21', '2026-04-08 18:59:21', 'en', 'neutral', 'XLE', '', 'Seeking Alpha', 'https://seekingalpha.com/news/4572831-us-shale-drillers-expected-to-finally-boost-crude-production-on-war-driven-price-rally?utm_source=feed_news_all&utm_medium=referral&feed_item_type=news', '', 'approved') ON CONFLICT (id) DO NOTHING;
